query: SELECT ce.id as enrollment_id, ce.userId, ce.bundleId, cb.id as bundle_table_id, cb.name as bundle_name FROM course_enrollments ce LEFT JOIN course_bundles cb ON ce.bundleId = cb.id WHERE ce.bundleId IS NOT NULL ORDER BY ce.userId;
